## How to apply (until CLI is linked)

1. Open League project SQL Editor in the Supabase dashboard.
2. Paste the migration SQL and run it.
3. Or use `psql` / Supabase CLI against League with a real `DATABASE_URL` / linked project.

## Agent requirements before claiming migrations applied

- Confirm target project ref is League.
- Prefer idempotent SQL (`if not exists`, etc.).
